    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Collections of related objects are defined in MIB modules.  It may be useful to define the acceptable lower-bounds of implementation, along with the actual level of implementation achieved.  It is the purpose of this document to define the notation used for these purposes. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
